race.comment: CARDONETTE (4) is unlucky to still be a maiden finishing runner-up in both starts to date and strikes a very winnable contest here. Thompson stays in the stirrups and should be going one better against this lot. YOUMEANDDUPRE (5) resumes here but the form he showed last campaign was good enough for a race of this calibre. Revved up for this winning two recent trials and should be right there at the business end. OUR GIRL SCARLETT (11) just missed the placings in town when resuming and will have come on with that run now in the locker. Top-three candidate. ELUSIVE DOMINA (9) best of the rest while fresh.
